01:13:04,214 --> 01:13:06,180
Ok.

1635
01:13:06,282 --> 01:13:08,950
- Ta-da!
- Yeah! All right, well done!

1636
01:13:09,052 --> 01:13:10,451
Let's get this party going.
Come on!

1637
01:13:10,553 --> 01:13:11,652
Give me a ho, ho, ho!

1638
01:13:11,755 --> 01:13:12,854
All: Ho, ho, ho!

1639
