we had a long talk.

1681
01:14:55,792 --> 01:14:59,060
He told me that he knew
how he was too hard on you,

1682
01:14:59,162 --> 01:15:02,663
that he always just wanted
what was best for you.

1683
01:15:02,765 --> 01:15:05,066
