I like this new tradition.

1756
01:18:13,172 --> 01:18:16,507
That is my dad's tool belt.

1757
01:18:16,609 --> 01:18:18,109
That way you'll know
you'll always have the tools

1758
01:18:18,211 --> 01:18:19,710
